rComments: Lectures extremely quickly, makes it very hard to take good notes. Wrote his midterm to take more time than was provided, so the majority of the class didn't finish, a fact he seemed proud of. In lab periods, when doing time-sensitive experiments, he will often come stand between you and the fume hood to talk, eating up time you need to finish.
He goes very fast during lecture and don't time to student to copy everything from slides and also won't let student take pics. Also has very bad attitude.

Definitely a character. Actually a decent lecture prof. His slides are dense and confusing on their own, but his lectures lend them clarity. His midterm was easy. As a lab demonstrator he can be a bit unsettling, and he really likes to talk, but if you actually listen you can learn some useful techniques. He'll answer questions helpfully if asked.
He's not the nicest, but you gotta admit, his midterms in 238 are extremely easy.

Worst prof ever, so mean spirited, always gets mad during lab or breathes down your neck which therefore makes you drop things out of nervousness. He's so arrogant and takes forever doing simple demos in lab to waste as much of your precious lab time in a class where staying late gets you marks deducted. Hes not understanding or considerate. WORST
